<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <% include ./head.ejs %>
  <body>
    <div class="page" style="background-color: #3A7959;">
      <div class="page" style="height: 100%; background-image: url('/images/main.jpg'); background-size: cover; filter: brightness(40%); opacity: 0.8;">
      </div>
      <div class="scroll-downs">
        <div class="mousey">
          <div class="scroller"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="page" style="background-color: #3A7959; height: auto;">
      <div class="page-content">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col">
            <div class="card" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-anchor-placement="top-center">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="card-title">오늘의 퀴즈</h3>
                <p class="card-text">오늘의 퀴즈를 풀고 부대 랭킹을 올려보세요.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-4"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-4"></div>
          <div class="col">
            <div class="card" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-anchor-placement="top-center">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="card-title">대전 모드</h3>
                <p class="card-text">유저들과 대결을 통해 부대 랭킹을 올려보세요.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col">
            <div class="card" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-anchor-placement="top-center">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="card-title">부대 랭킹</h3>
                <p class="card-text">부대 랭킹을 확인해보세요.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-4"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-4"></div>
          <div class="col">
            <div class="card" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-anchor-placement="top-center">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="card-title">마이페이지</h3>
                <p class="card-text">오답 노트를 통해 틀렸던 퀴즈를 복습하고 개인 전적을 확인해보세요.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="page" style="background-color: #3A7959;">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-2"></div>
        <div class="col-8">
          <div class="row" style="margin-top: 25vh;">
            <div class="col">
              <div class="card" style="height: 50vh; margin-bottom: 16px;">
                <h3 class="card-title">Notice</h3><br>
                <div class="notice important">
                  <span>중요 공지입니다.</span>
                  <span style="vertical-align: middle; float: right;">
                    <span class="material-icons-round" style="vertical-align: middle;">visibility</span> 1000&nbsp;&nbsp;
                    <span class="material-icons-round" style="vertical-align: middle;">calendar_today</span> 2022-07-28
                  </span>
                </div>
                <% for(var i = 0; i < 5; i++ ) {%>
                <div class="notice">
                  <span>공지입니다.</span>
                  <span style="vertical-align: middle; float: right;">
                    <span class="material-icons-round" style="vertical-align: middle;">visibility</span> 1000&nbsp;&nbsp;
                    <span class="material-icons-round" style="vertical-align: middle;">calendar_today</span> 2022-07-28
                  </span>
                </div>
                <% } %>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-4">
              <form action="signin" method="post">
                <div class="card" style="height: 50vh; margin-bottom: 16px;">
                  <h3 class="card-title">Login</h3><br>
                  <p class="card-subtitle" style="text-align: start;">아이디</p>
                  <input class="card-input-text" type="text" name="uid" placeholder="아이디를 입력하세요."><br>
                  <p class="card-subtitle" style="text-align: start;">비밀번호</p>
                  <input class="card-input-text" type="password" name="upw" placeholder="비밀번호를 입력하세요."><br>
                  <input class="card-btn-signin" type="submit" value="로그인">
                  <p class="card-subtitle" style="text-align: start;">아이디가 없으신가요? <span ></span></p>
                  <button class="card-btn-signin" type="button" onclick="location.href='/signup' ">회원가입하기</button>
                </div>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-2"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
  <script src="/javascripts/scroll.js"></script>
</html>
